msgid "blob globs"
msgstr "粘液團塊"

#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid "blob_grow_base"
msgid_plural "blob_grow_bases"
msgstr[0] "粘液生長基體"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blob_grow_base'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'growing bladed mass', 'str_pl': 'growing bladed
#. mass'}
#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid ""
"Not quite fully grown, this blob requires nourishment to fully develop."
msgstr "尚未完全成熟，這個粘液團需要養分才能完全發育。"

#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gel razor"
msgid_plural "gel razors"
msgstr[0] "凝膠剃刀"

#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid ""
"A living blob turned into an autonomous weapon.  Instead of calcifying large"
" amounts of calcified teeth, it has instead calcified a single large blade-"
"like mass; which it uses defensively and offensively.  The amorphous mass "
"can be shaped and attached at your touch, but the weapon itself is inert "
"without something to control it."
msgstr ""
"一個活體粘液團轉變成了自主武器。它沒有鈣化大量鈣化牙齒，而是鈣化了一個單一的大型刀刃狀物質；用於防禦和攻擊。這種無定形物質可以在你的觸摸下塑形並附著，但武器本身在沒有控制物的情況下是惰性的。"

#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "melee"
msgstr "近戰"

#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid "growing bladed mass"
msgid_plural "growing bladed mass"
msgstr[0] "生長的刀刃物質"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'growing bladed mass', 'str_pl': 'growing
#. bladed mass'}.
#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid "The blob balloons to full size."
msgstr "粘液團膨脹到完整大小。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'growing bladed mass', 'str_pl':
#. 'growing bladed mass'}.
#: .\blaze_blob.json
msgid "It hasn't grown enough yet.."
msgstr "它長得還不夠大.."

